properties.description:
Farnborough (Yeppoon) – bushfire as at 11.30am Wed 27 Jan        Multiple Queensland Fire and Emergency Services (QFES) crews remain on scene at the fire in Farnborough. The fire is burning between Fishing Creek Road and Kelly’s Landing Road and smoke will continue to impact nearby residents in Maryvale, Woodbury and Byfield. Residents are asked to close windows and doors and if suffering from a respiratory condition, keep medications close by. Motorists should drive with caution and to conditions. If residents are concerned their property is under threat, they are advised to call Triple Zero (000) immediately.  
Response Time: 20210114153529
Vehicles on Scene:5
Vehicles on Route: 0
